266
00:23:52,208 --> 00:23:59,529
really complicated when you're doing mixed housing with people who are in mixed income levels and all walks of life.

267
00:23:59,669 --> 00:24:01,370
And there's a lot to manage with that.

268
00:24:01,410 --> 00:24:06,411
And then it becomes a really high priority to manage the substance use disorder and maybe mental health issues.

269
00:24:06,511 --> 00:24:11,152
So it's really great that you're doing a project like this for people who are local.

270
00:24:11,752 --> 00:24:13,412
