278
00:25:10,725 --> 00:25:12,927
And literally, it's walking distance from Medford Square.

279
00:25:12,947 --> 00:25:14,549
It's like a minute and a half up the street.

280
00:25:14,689 --> 00:25:16,571
So anybody can get here.

281
00:25:16,611 --> 00:25:18,553
And that's the beauty of where it's located.

282
00:25:18,893 --> 00:25:21,776
Where, like I said, when it was in Belmont, getting there was difficult.

283
00:25:21,796 --> 00:25:24,058
There's a lot of people that they lose their ability to drive.

284
00:25:25,520 --> 00:25:36,876
